This is a placeholder entry, which I will use to make a list of Sanskrit sutra
                    names to be applied consistently throughout. *Candragarbha-vaipulya-sūtra;
                    Śaptaśatikā-prajñāpāramitā; Mahāratnakūṭa-sūtra;
                    *Mahāvaipulya-mahāsaṃnipāta-sūtra; Pañcaviṃśatisāhasrikā-prajñāpāramitā;
                    Mahā-prajñāpāramitā-śāstra, *Mahā-prajñāpāramitā-hṛdaya-sūtra
